data.description: This home has been perfectly maintained along with many upgrades that have been completed recently. Sellers have installed a new HVAC system in 2022 along with new ductwork, a new tankless hot water heater in 2021, new fans, toilets, new ice maker installed in kitchen, and brand new flooring installed through majority of the home. Lots of flex spaces allow for this layout to be exactly what your family needs! 4 Bedrooms, 2.5 Baths, a huge living room with vaulted ceilings, formal dining, sunroom, and a large eat in kitchen. Formal dining room is currently being used as a second living area. Utility room has a sink, storage, plus space for a second fridge. The spacious sunroom sits between the main living area and the back patio and would serve as a fantastic workout room, playroom, or pool room area. The gorgeous in ground pool has been updated with a new pump and filter system that will be primed and perfect for next summer! Sellers will give a $5,000 allowance with acceptable offer.
